WKT: The Russian occupiers continue to convert educational institutions in the temporarily occupied settlements of Ukraine into military medical institutions. In particular
name: the invaders turned a secondary school in the village of Azov in the Zaporizhzhya region and a preschool in the village of Gladkivka in the Kherson region into field hospitals. About 50 occupiers with injuries of varying degrees of severity are being treated there.
